snippet.title: The River Why - The Movie Trailer
snippet.description: This is the trailer for the movie "The River Why", starring Zach Gilford, Amber Heard, Kathleen Quinlan, Dallas Roberts, William Devane and William Hurt. The feature length movie was completed in 2010 and is based on the acclaimed novel of the same name. Directed by Matthew Leutwyler. Produced by Kristi Denton Cohen and Peloton Productions in association with Ambush Entertainment and StopTime Productions. Script by Thomas A. Cohen and John Jay Osborn, Jr. Director of Photography: Crash.
